title: NAIA Men's & Women's Cross Country National Championships
text:
NAIA Men's & Women's Cross Country National Championships Where 
10:30 a.m. Saturday, Nov. 21, 2015 Categories 
Events, Outdoors | Recreation, Sports o NAIA Men’s & Women’s Cross Country National Championships o Nov. 21 at McAlpine Creek Park o Men’s 8K race: 10:30 a.m. o Women’s 5K race: 11:30 a.m. o Post-race awards ceremony: app. 1 p.m. o FREE event o Go to www.NAIA.org for more information o NAIA (small college) national championship in men's and women's cross country. Over 600 runners competing for the ultimate price in the NAIA.
